strong\u003eTamba tea bowl location\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Assassins-Creed-Shadows-tea-bowls-Tamba-Kameyama.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0,0,100,100\" data-pswp-height=\"1080\" data-pswp-width=\"1920\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Assassin’s Creed Shadows Tamba tea bowls location\" data-chromatic=\"ignore\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"(max-width: 639px) 100vw, (max-width: 1023px) 50vw, 700px\" srcset=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Assassins-Creed-Shadows-tea-bowls-Tamba-Kameyama.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=256 256w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Assassins-Creed-Shadows-tea-bowls-Tamba-Kameyama.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=376 376w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Assassins-Creed-Shadows-tea-bowls-Tamba-Kameyama.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=384 384w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Assassins-Creed-Shadows-tea-bowls-Tamba-Kameyama.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=415 415w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Assassins-Creed-Shadows-tea-bowls-Tamba-Kameyama.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=480 480w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Assassins-Creed-Shadows-tea-bowls-Tamba-Kameyama.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=540 540w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Assassins-Creed-Shadows-tea-bowls-Tamba-Kameyama.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=640 640w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Assassins-Creed-Shadows-tea-bowls-Tamba-Kameyama.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=750 750w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Assassins-Creed-Shadows-tea-bowls-Tamba-Kameyama.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=828 828w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Assassins-Creed-Shadows-tea-bowls-Tamba-Kameyama.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1080 1080w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Assassins-Creed-Shadows-tea-bowls-Tamba-Kameyama.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1200 1200w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Assassins-Creed-Shadows-tea-bowls-Tamba-Kameyama.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1440 1440w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Assassins-Creed-Shadows-tea-bowls-Tamba-Kameyama.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1920 1920w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Assassins-Creed-Shadows-tea-bowls-Tamba-Kameyama.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2048 2048w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Assassins-Creed-Shadows-tea-bowls-Tamba-Kameyama.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400 2400w\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Assassins-Creed-Shadows-tea-bowls-Tamba-Kameyama.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ccite\u003eImage: Ubisoft Quebec/Ubisoft via Polygon\u003c/cite\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe \u003cstrong\u003eSimple Tea Bowl Collection\u003c/strong\u003e can be purchased from the ornament merchant in \u003cstrong\u003eKameyama \u003c/strong\u003ein southeastern \u003cstrong\u003eTamba\u003c/strong\u003e. You’ll find the vendor on the south side of town.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp id=\"tk-tea-bowl-location\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFinal tea bowl set location\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe final tea bowl set is a reward for killing \u003cstrong\u003eThe Wise\u003c/strong\u003e — one of the Shinbakufu — as part of the main story. (This is also a spoiler-adjacent hint to The Wise’s identity.) Once you complete the sub-quests and kill The Wise, you’ll get the \u003cstrong\u003eClassic Tea Bowl Collection\u003c/strong\u003e automatically.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp id=\"tea-bowls-for-rikyu-rewards\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003e‘Tea Bowls for Rikyu’ rewards\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe first set of bowls you bring to Sen no Rikyu will unlock the \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/assassins-creed-shadows-guides/541616/tea-room-how-to-unlock-build\"\u003eTea Room\u003c/a\u003e for your \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/assassins-creed-shadows-guides/540840/hideout-rooms-upgrades-best-build-first\"\u003eHideout\u003c/a\u003e. You’ll get bits of dialogue for the others, but no reward.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhen you turn them all in, you’ll receive \u003cstrong\u003e1,100 XP\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp id=\"should-you-invite-enemies-or-friends\"\u003e\u003ch2\u003eShould you invite enemies or friends?\u003c/h2\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Assassins-Creed-Shadows-tea-bowls-end.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0,0,100,100\" data-pswp-