w=828 828w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Assassins-Creed-Shadows-tea-bowls-end.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1080 1080w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Assassins-Creed-Shadows-tea-bowls-end.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1200 1200w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Assassins-Creed-Shadows-tea-bowls-end.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1440 1440w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Assassins-Creed-Shadows-tea-bowls-end.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=1920 1920w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Assassins-Creed-Shadows-tea-bowls-end.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2048 2048w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Assassins-Creed-Shadows-tea-bowls-end.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400 2400w\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/03/Assassins-Creed-Shadows-tea-bowls-end.jpg?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ccite\u003eImage: Ubisoft Quebec/Ubisoft via Polygon\u003c/cite\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eYou’ll also get invited to Sen no Rikyu’s first tea ceremony in his new tea house. You’ll get the choice to \u003cstrong\u003einvite enemies\u003c/strong\u003e or \u003cstrong\u003einvite friends\u003c/strong\u003e. If you invite your enemies, you’ll get a new quest named, \u003cstrong\u003e“Fish in a Barrel”\u003c/strong\u003e where several of your assassination targets — like The Iron Hand or other, non-Shinbakufu leaders — show up at Rikyu’s. Your task is just to sneak around the tea house’s courtyard and assassinate them. This, however, goes against everything the tea ceremony is about and will upset Sen no Rikyu.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eIt’s better to just have a tea ceremony with your friends.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eFor more \u003cem\u003eAssassin’s Creed Shadows\u003c/em\u003e guides, see our running lists of \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/assassins-creed-shadows-guides/541459/lost-pages-temples-locations-all-list-where-to-find\"\u003eLost Pages\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/assassins-creed-shadows-guides/541590/kuji-kiri-locations-all-list-maps-where-to-find\"\u003eKuji-kiri\u003c/a\u003e, and \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/assassins-creed-shadows-guides/541239/armor-sets-all-list-locations-how-to-get\"\u003earmor\u003c/a\u003e locations. Or see our full \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/assassins-creed-shadows-guides/541235/walkthrough-main-missions-best-target-order\"\u003e\u003cem\u003eAssassin’s Creed Shadows\u003c/em\u003e walkthrough\u003c/a\u003e, and our guides on how to get all \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/assassins-creed-shadows-guides/542428/companions-allies-how-to-recruit-all-list\"\u003ecompanions\u003c/a\u003e and \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/assassins-creed-shadows-guides/542414/romance-options-all-list-how-to-unlock\"\u003eromance options\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
